data:
To,     Date:         01-07.2022

Jobin Baby,

India. 



CONFIRMATION LETTER FOR PROBATION PERIOD‌


  

SUB: Appointment letter for probation period in Dowell Research

 ‌

 Dear Jobin Baby, 

‌

We are pleased to inform you that you have been qualified for the probation period provided on acceptance of the below-given conditions. 


You will be appointed as a candidate in the ‘Mathematical modelling department’ with effect from 22nd, June 2022 for a period of 6 months with the stipend of Rs. 5000 Per Month.


CONDITIONS:

  • Your working hours will be 9:30 am to 5:30 pm from Monday to Saturday.

  • You are not entitled to take leave without prior permission.

  • You have to submit an activity report to your manager on a daily basis, failure of this will affect your Monthly Performance.

  • There will be Monthly Performance Evaluations and unsatisfactory performance may lead to termination of the probation.

  • You are not permitted to take paid or unpaid jobs with any other companies/firms/individuals during this period.

  • You are not permitted to disclose any official information related to your job to the public.

  • This is not an employment contract. There is no employee-employer relationship during the probation period.

  • Based on your performance during the probation period, the company shall issue you the offer letter for further employment.  

  • While accepting this letter, you have to update your LinkedIn profile mentioning the details of your probation period in Dowell Research Pte. Ltd.

  • If you are not found suitable for the job, your appointment will be terminated at the discretion of the company and in case of such termination, you will have no right or claim against the company.

  • You shall abide by the terms and conditions of the standing orders and the rules of the company as in force from time to time.

You are requested to abide by the general rules and policies of the company during the period of probation.‌

You will be given a certificate after successfully completing your probation period in this company.  

 Please sign this letter as an indication of your acceptance, not later than two days.                                      

Thanks & Regards

For D’Well Research
Authorized Signatory

HR Department
              Haritha S Nair
(Executive, Finance & Admin dept)
